===Noun===
'''ixnay'''

# No.

===Verb, transitive===
'''ixnay''' (present tense only)

# (''Used in an imperative'') Do not do or talk about (something).
#: ''Ixnay on the "W-A-L-K" while the dogs can hear you.''

